  "id": "api/core/TemplateRef",
  "title": "TemplateRef",
  "contents": "\n\n<article>\n  <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/core/src/linker/template_ref.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L11-L57\" aria-label=\"建议修改\" title=\"建议修改\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/6.1.0/packages/core/src/linker/template_ref.ts#L11-L57\" aria-label=\"查看源码\" title=\"查看源码\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n    <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n      {\n        \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n        \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n        \"itemListElement\": [\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn//api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/core\", \"name\": \"@angular/core\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/core/TemplateRef\", \"name\": \"TemplateRef\" } }\n        ]\n      }\n    </script>\n      <a href=\"/api\">API</a> / <a href=\"api/core\">@angular/core</a>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"templateref\">TemplateRef<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/TemplateRef#templateref\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label class\">class</label>\n    \n    \n    <label class=\"api-status-label stable\">稳定</label>\n    \n  </header>\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n    \n  <p class=\"short-description\"></p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Represents an Embedded Template that can be used to instantiate Embedded Views.</p>\n<p translation-result=\"\">代表一个可用来实例化内嵌视图的内嵌模板。</p>\n<p></p>\n  \n\n  \n\n  \n  <section class=\"class-overview\">\n<code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" linenums=\"false\">\nabstract class <a href=\"api/core/TemplateRef\" class=\"code-anchor\">TemplateRef</a>&#x3C;C> {\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/TemplateRef#elementRef\">abstract get elementRef: ElementRef</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/TemplateRef#createEmbeddedView\">abstract createEmbeddedView(context: C): EmbeddedViewRef&#x3C;C></a>\n}\n</code-example>\n\n  \n  \n\n</section>\n\n\n  \n\n  \n  \n  \n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">说明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/TemplateRef#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p translation-origin=\"off\">You can access a <code><a href=\"api/core/TemplateRef\" class=\"code-anchor\">TemplateRef</a></code>, in two ways. Via a directive placed on a <code>&#x3C;ng-template></code> element\n(or directive prefixed with <code>*</code>) and have the <code><a href=\"api/core/TemplateRef\" class=\"code-anchor\">TemplateRef</a></code> for this Embedded View injected into\nthe constructor of the directive using the <code><a href=\"api/core/TemplateRef\" class=\"code-anchor\">TemplateRef</a></code> Token. Alternatively you can query for\nthe <code><a href=\"api/core/TemplateRef\" class=\"code-anchor\">TemplateRef</a></code> from a Component or a Directive via <a href=\"api/core/Query\"><code>Query</code></a>.</p>\n<p translation-result=\"\">你可以用两种方式访问 <code><a href=\"api/core/TemplateRef\" class=\"code-anchor\">TemplateRef</a></code>。通过一个放在 <code>&#x3C;ng-template></code> 元素上的指令（或带有 <code>*</code> 前缀的指令），\n可以用 <code><a href=\"api/core/TemplateRef\" class=\"code-anchor\">TemplateRef</a></code> 作为令牌把它的内嵌视图注入到该指令的构造函数中。\n你还可以在组件或指令中通过 <a href=\"api/core/Query\"><code>Query</code></a> 来查询 <code><a href=\"api/core/TemplateRef\" class=\"code-anchor\">TemplateRef</a></code>。</p>\n<p translation-origin=\"off\">To instantiate Embedded Views based on a Template, use <a href=\"api/core/ViewContainerRef#\">createEmbeddedView</a>, which will create the View and attach it to the View Container.</p>\n<p translation-result=\"\">要想实例化一个基于模板的内嵌视图，可使用 <a href=\"api/core/ViewContainerRef#\">createEmbeddedView</a>，该方法会创建一个视图，\n并把它挂到所属的视图容器中。</p>\n\n</section>\n\n\n  \n\n\n  \n\n  \n\n  \n\n<section class=\"instance-properties\">\n  <h2 id=\"属性\">属性<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/TemplateRef#属性\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table property-table\">\n    <thead>\n      <tr>\n        <th>属性名</th>\n        <th>类型</th>\n        <th>说明</th>\n      </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n    \n      <tr class=\"instance-property\">\n        <td><a id=\"elementRef\"></a>elementRef</td>\n        <td><label class=\"property-type-label\"><code><a href=\"api/core/ElementRef\" class=\"code-anchor\">ElementRef</a></code></label></td>\n        <td><span class=\"read-only-property\">只读</span>\n          <p translation-origin=\"off\">The location in the View where the Embedded View logically belongs to.</p>\n<p translation-result=\"\">内嵌视图在其所属视图中的位置。</p>\n\n          <p translation-origin=\"off\">The data-binding and injection contexts of Embedded Views created from this <code><a href=\"api/core/TemplateRef\" class=\"code-anchor\">TemplateRef</a></code>\ninherit from the contexts of this location.</p>\n<p translation-result=\"\">对于从这个 <code><a href=\"api/core/TemplateRef\" class=\"code-anchor\">TemplateRef</a></code> 创建的内嵌视图，其数据绑定和依赖注入的上下文是从当前位置的上下文中继承而来的。</p>\n<p translation-origin=\"off\">Typically new Embedded Views are attached to the View Container of this location, but in\nadvanced use-cases, the View can be attached to a different container while keeping the\ndata-binding and injection context from the original location.</p>\n<p translation-result=\"\">通常，新的内嵌视图会被附加到当前位置的视图容器中，但是在一些高级用例中，该视图可能被附加到别的容器中，\n同时还保留原位置的数据绑定和依赖注入上下文。</p>\n\n          \n        </td>\n    </tr>\n    \n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n</section>\n\n  \n\n<section class=\"instance-methods\">\n  <h2 id=\"方法\">方法<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/TemplateRef#方法\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  \n    <a id=\"createEmbeddedView\"></a>\n<table class=\"is-full-width method-table instance-method\">\n  <thead><tr><th>\n    <div class=\"with-github-links\">\n      <h3 id=\"createembeddedview\">\n        createEmbeddedView()\n        \n      <a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/TemplateRef#createembeddedview\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n      <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/core/src/linker/template_ref.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L55-L56\" aria-label=\"建议修改\" title=\"建议修改\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/6.1.0/packages/core/src/linker/template_ref.ts#L55-L56\" aria-label=\"查看源码\" title=\"查看源码\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n    </div>\n  </th></tr></thead>\n  <tbody>\n    \n  \n    <tr>\n      <td>\n        \n\n<code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" linenums=\"false\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">abstract createEmbeddedView(context: C): <a href=\"api/core/EmbeddedViewRef\" class=\"code-anchor\">EmbeddedViewRef</a>&#x3C;C></code-example>\n\n<h4 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"参数\">参数</h4>\n<table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table instance-method-overload-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n  \n    <tr class=\"instance-method-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\"><a id=\"\"></a>context</td>\n      \n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n            <p translation-origin=\"off\">Type: <code>C</code>.</p>\n      \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n\n<h4 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"返回值\">返回值</h4>\n<p translation-origin=\"off\"><code><a href=\"api/core/EmbeddedViewRef\" class=\"code-anchor\">EmbeddedViewRef&#x3C;C></a></code></p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n\n  \n\n  \n    </tbody>\n</table>\n\n  \n</section>\n\n\n  \n\n\n  \n\n\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/common\n - api/common/NgForOf\n - api/common/NgIf\n - api/common/NgTemplateOutlet\n - api/core\n - api/core/EmbeddedViewRef\n - api/core/ViewContainerRef\n - guide/glossary\n - guide/structural-directives\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core\n - api/core/ElementRef\n - api/core/EmbeddedViewRef\n - api/core/Query\n - api/core/TemplateRef#createEmbeddedView\n - api/core/TemplateRef#createembeddedview\n - api/core/TemplateRef#description\n - api/core/TemplateRef#elementRef\n - api/core/TemplateRef#templateref\n - api/core/TemplateRef#属性\n - api/core/TemplateRef#方法\n - api/core/ViewContainerRef#\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/core/src/linker/template_ref.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L11-L57\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/core/src/linker/template_ref.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L55-L56\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/6.1.0/packages/core/src/linker/template_ref.ts#L11-L57\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/6.1.0/packages/core/src/linker/template_ref.ts#L55-L56\n-->"
